      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;x-recon---a-utility-for-detecting-webpage-inputs-and-conducting-xss-scans&#34;&gt;X-Recon - A Utility For Detecting Webpage Inputs And Conducting XSS Scans&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- raw HTML omitted --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- raw HTML omitted --&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;a-utility-for-identifying-web-page-inputs-and-conducting-xss-scanning&#34;&gt;A utility for identifying web page inputs and conducting XSS scanning.&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;features&#34;&gt;Features:&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Subdomain Discovery:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Retrieves relevant &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.kitploit.com/search/label/Subdomains&#34; title=&#34;subdomains&#34;&gt;subdomains&lt;/a&gt; for the target website and consolidates them into a &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.kitploit.com/search/label/Whitelist&#34; title=&#34;whitelist&#34;&gt;whitelist&lt;/a&gt;. These &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.kitploit.com/search/label/Subdomains&#34; title=&#34;subdomains&#34;&gt;subdomains&lt;/a&gt; can be utilized during the &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.kitploit.com/search/label/Scraping&#34; title=&#34;scraping&#34;&gt;scraping&lt;/a&gt; process.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Site-wide Link Discovery:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Collects all links throughout the website based on the provided whitelist and the specified &lt;code&gt;max_depth&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
